Wingold Lawrence https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wingold_Lawrence 0 Wingold Lawrence (1874–1938) was a British actor. Lawrence emerged as a prominent stage actor of the London theatre. He also enjoyed a brief film career, with leading roles in films such as Eugene Aram (1914) and Mysteries of London (1915). Wingold_Lawrence ( 1874 – 1938 ) was a_British_actor .
